1	//! Goal state manager.
2	//!
3	//! Owns the shared [`GoalState`] for every active goal, protected by
4	//! `Arc<RwLock<GoalStateStore>>`. All sessions working on the same goal
5	//! read/write this shared state. Progress updates are broadcast via
6	//! `tokio::broadcast` to all subscribers.
7	
